ISLAMABAD, Jan 7 (APP): Ambassador of Kingdom of Saudi Arabia (KSA) Nawaf Saeed Al Malkiy visited Naval Headquarters (NHQ) and met Chief of the Naval Staff (CNS) Admiral Muhammad Amjad Khan Niazi.
Both the dignitaries discussed matters of mutual interest, bilateral collaborations and maritime security in the region, said the Directorate General of Pakistan Navy in a tweet.
